wiki.summary: "(It Goes Like) Nanana" is a song by South Korean DJ and producer Peggy Gou, released as the lead single from her forthcoming debut album on 15 June 2023. It is her first single to be issued through XL Recordings. The song debuted at number 14 on the UK Singles Chart dated 23 June 2023, making it Gou's first UK chart entry. A week later the single entered the UK top 10 at number 5. Read more on Last.fm.
